The control toolbox contains modules that are useful across all controllers.

    Maintainer status: maintained
    Maintainer: Bence Magyar <bence.magyar.robotics AT gmail DOT com>
    Author: Melonee Wise, Sachin Chitta, John Hsu
    License: BSD
    Bug / feature tracker: https://github.com/ros-controls/control_toolbox/issues
    Source: git https://github.com/ros-controls/control_toolbox.git (branch: melodic-devel)

This package contains several C++ classes useful in writing controllers, and so the main documentation can be found on the control_toolbox doxygen page. 
